distance_type.title: Distance Calculation Method
distance_type.description:
How distances are calculated when distance_matrix is not explicitly provided. Available options:
- EUCLIDEAN: Straight-line distance between coordinates
- MANHATTAN: Sum of absolute differences in latitude and longitude
- OSRM: Real road network distance using Open Source Routing Machine. OSRM supports only Korean region and provides the most accurate travel distances.
